{"3976330": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Life of Guy - Chapter 1", "steam_appid": 3976330, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3976330/extras/290f2bf1295fc0d2f4c9f369f5be3fc8.avif?t=1773889574\" width=1560 height=878 /></span>Life of Guy is a light-hearted sandbox adult visual novel about a man and his monster.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game takes place in a fictional world where regular humans and supernatural entities (known as Specials) live side by side albeit with obvious frictions due to their innate differences. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The main story centers around Guy who has been possessed by a Lust Goddess. He must now navigate his new cursed life and befriend many supernatural characters in an effort to learn how to rid himself of his demonic passenger and return to his normal life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is choice-driven and features various side quests with over 40 unique characters for the player to build relationships with. It's also pretty funny at times, I promise. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A NOTE ON THIS GAME'S RELEASE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Life of Guy - Chapter 1</strong> is the first part of a larger, episodic story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you purchase the game, you will get the complete Chapter 1. The rest of the story is already in active development and will be released episodically as <strong>100% FREE UPDATES</strong> for everyone who owns the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your single purchase grants you access to the entire saga, no matter how big it gets.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I am fully committed to completing the entire story arc. The current outline is for at least three chapters, but possibly more.<strong> </strong>Whether it's 3 chapters or 5, all future story chapters will be delivered as free updates. Your purchase directly funds the development of this future content. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Please try the free demo, there's enough content to give you a good idea of what the game is like before you buy.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you for your support, and welcome to the Life of Guy! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3976330/extras/657a6e7b3c47e49816b4c2cee619bf06.poster.avif?t=1773889574\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3976330/extras/657a6e7b3c47e49816b4c2cee619bf06.webm?t=1773889574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3976330/extras/aff15e02f833a3d6266cd399cce2e424.poster.avif?t=1773889574\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3976330/extras/aff15e02f833a3d6266cd399cce2e424.webm?t=1773889574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3976330/extras/06942624a3a460a3b1a419e8acdca20a.poster.avif?t=1773889574\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3976330/extras/06942624a3a460a3b1a419e8acdca20a.webm?t=1773889574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_i